column1: #text=I was invited to my friend 's housewarming party this weekend and although we were n't asked to bring anything I wanted to bring something .
#text=Knowing that my friend loves chocolate cake I decided to bake her one .
#text=I went to the kitchen and grabbed a large bowl , a whisk , a cake pan , and the ingredients for the cake .
#text=I went to preheat the oven and in the meantime I grabbed the bowl and added chocolate cake mix , eggs , milk , and butter .
#text=I mixed the ingredients with my whisk until my desired consistency .
#text=I buttered the inside of the cake pan then added the cake batter into the pan .
#text=Once the oven preheated and was ready I put the cake into the oven .
#text=An hour later the cake was ready .
#text=I let it cool a bit then started to frost the cake with frosting I purchased from the store .
#text=I added some strawberries on top for decoration .
